.renaissancecapital.com/Profile/TEM/Tempus-AI/IPO\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noopener noopener\">Given the stock's 36% gain since its IPO</a>, we think that it is</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1213764535/image_1213764535.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743128-time-is-up-for-tempus-ai-with-ipo-lockup-expiration", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 03:19:18"}, {"id": "4743127", "title": "Be Cautious When Others Are No Longer Fearful", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1200508619/image_1200508619.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Stock Market Crash and Escape - Global Business Strategy Exchange\" data-id=\"1200508619\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"8000px\" height=\"5000px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1200508619/image_1200508619.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1200508619/image_1200508619.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1200508619/image_1200508619.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1200508619/image_1200508619.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1200508619/image_1200508619.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1200508619/image_1200508619.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1200508619/image_1200508619.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1200508619/image_1200508619.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">sefa ozel</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><span>Last week, we discussed the \"<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741532-prepare-for-the-trump-rally-phase-two\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741532-prepare-for-the-trump-rally-phase-two\" target=\"_blank\">Trump Bump</a>\" and how the upcoming political and economic environment may create a favorable intermediate and longer-term atmosphere for high-quality stocks and other risk assets. The S&amp;P 500 \"SPX\" (</span><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SP500\" class=\"ticker-link\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SP500\" target=\"_blank\">SP500</a><span>) has surged since the</span></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1200508619/image_1200508619.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743127-be-cautious-when-others-are-no-longer-fearful", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 03:04:47"}, {"id": "4743126", "title": "Asana: Stickiness Of AI Studio Could Lead The Turnaround - Initiating With Buy", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155380391/image_155380391.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"The Passion of One Ignites New Ideas, Social Movements, Change\" data-id=\"155380391\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155380391/image_155380391.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155380391/image_155380391.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155380391/image_155380391.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155380391/image_155380391.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155380391/image_155380391.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155380391/image_155380391.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155380391/image_155380391.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155380391/image_155380391.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">JamesBrey/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>We're initiating our coverage on Asana, Inc. (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ASAN\" title=\"Asana, Inc.\">ASAN</a></span>) with a Buy after its recent <a href=\"https://investors.asana.com/financials/quarterly-results\" rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://investors.asana.com/financials/quarterly-results\" target=\"_blank\">3QFY25</a> earnings triggered the stock to close 43% higher the day after, on Friday, with Wall Street taking notice of Asana's new AI Studio and 89% gross profit</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155380391/image_155380391.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743126-asana-stickiness-of-ai-studio-could-lead-the-turnaround-initiating-with-buy", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 02:41:31"}, {"id": "4743129", "title": "Opposite Day To Start The Week", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/160616076/image_160616076.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Calculator and charts\" data-id=\"160616076\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5472px\" height=\"3648px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/160616076/image_160616076.jpg?io=getty-c-w153