eck of luxury hotel suite at sunset\" data-id=\"1363844060\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1363844060/image_1363844060.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1363844060/image_1363844060.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1363844060/image_1363844060.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1363844060/image_1363844060.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1363844060/image_1363844060.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1363844060/image_1363844060.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1363844060/image_1363844060.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1363844060/image_1363844060.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Thomas Barwick/DigitalVision via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>If you're like me, you've been scouring the stock market looking for good growth stocks to invest in that don't feel \"too late\" to get into. Many of the highest quality software and internet stocks have run up dramatically this year, some enjoying a doubling</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1363844060/image_1363844060.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743124-airbnb-tough-road-ahead-as-hotel-competitors-close-in-with-strong-bookings", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 01:50:21"}, {"id": "4743122", "title": "UnitedHealth Group CEO's Deat